A Priest Possessed His Wife To Keep Her Alive | Forsaken | Exorcism Horror Movie

When a Priest discovers his wife is deathly ill, he goes against his faith and uses his knowledge of exorcisms to possess her in order to save her life. His actions have now unleashed the vengeful souls of those he lost and they want revenge. 

2016.  Stars: Elias Alexandro, Micheal Catalano, David E. Cazares
